== About Green HK

People are lazy to bring plastic bottles to recycle bin. Always blaming that there is no collection point near his home nor office.

== Features

* Marker Manager
* Translating Address to Latitude and Longitude
  * To keep the code simple, recycle Bin location is not modifiable.
* Marker Filter (TODO)
* Focus on Marker (TODO)


== Getting Started

* <strike>Setup MongoDB</strike>
* <strike>mongoid.yml</strike>
* The data is quite static at the moment, will move data out from mongoDB to simply json
* Sign up for Google Map API Key

== Technology Applied

* Google API
* Geocoder

== Difficulties

* Data Source
* Quality of data
